### Conflicts
Reviewers, this pull request conflicts with the following ones:

* [#14918](https://drahtbot.github.io/bitcoin_core_issue_redirect/r/14918.html) (RPCHelpMan: Check default values are given at compile-time by MarcoFalke)
* [#14491](https://drahtbot.github.io/bitcoin_core_issue_redirect/r/14491.html) (Allow descriptor imports with importmulti by MeshCollider)
* [#14459](https://drahtbot.github.io/bitcoin_core_issue_redirect/r/14459.html) (More RPC help description fixes by ch4ot1c)

If you consider this pull request important, please also help to review the conflicting pull requests. Ideally, start with the one that should be merged first.
